Package: bhipconfig
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, iproute2
Description: Interactive Linux network control surface for servers
 A dependency-light terminal UI for live Linux network management.
 It wraps iproute2 and resolver tooling behind a safer menu-driven
 interface with rollback protection for disruptive changes.
